00:00:11.678 --> 00:00:14.723 position:50% align:center
[MAKOTO] When video sharing
sites first became a thing,

00:00:14.806 --> 00:00:16.975 position:50% align:center
they were small and irrelevant.

00:00:17.058 --> 00:00:20.937 position:50% align:center
Like mice darting under
the feet of dinosaurs.

00:00:21.021 --> 00:00:24.274 position:50% align:center
It was all about news,
books, and TV.

00:00:24.357 --> 00:00:28.486 position:50% align:center
Today, the old gods
are slowly going extinct.

00:00:28.570 --> 00:00:30.238 position:50% align:center
The mice are just fine.

00:00:30.321 --> 00:00:32.907 position:50% align:center
They've evolved into
giants themselves.

00:00:32.991 --> 00:00:34.951 position:50% align:center
But no matter how big you get,

00:00:35.035 --> 00:00:37.620 position:50% align:center
the fight to survive
is still a rat race.

00:00:37.704 --> 00:00:39.414 position:50% align:center
Another day, another game.

00:00:40.415 --> 00:00:43.168 position:50% align:center
[sighs]

00:00:43.251 --> 00:00:45.670 position:50% align:center
Did you know the Red Angels
have their own channel too?

00:00:45.754 --> 00:00:47.047 position:50% align:center
Look here!

00:00:47.130 --> 00:00:49.549 position:50% align:center
And people actually
make a living this way?

00:00:49.632 --> 00:00:50.717 position:50% align:center
[ZERO-ONE]
Of course.

00:00:50.800 --> 00:00:53.094 position:50% align:center
It's much more than
just a silly hobby.

00:00:53.178 --> 00:00:55.055 position:50% align:center
When schools ask their
students what they wanna be

00:00:55.138 --> 00:00:56.681 position:50% align:center
when they grow up now,

00:00:56.765 --> 00:00:59.267 position:50% align:center
pro content creator is
always high on the list.

00:00:59.351 --> 00:01:01.561 position:50% align:center
No way that pulling
stunts is a real career.

00:02:37.907 --> 00:02:39.659 position:50% align:center
[ZERO-ONE] There are a lot of
vid sites where you can earn

00:02:39.743 --> 00:02:42.078 position:50% align:center
a high payout, but the
most popular platform

00:02:42.162 --> 00:02:44.998 position:50% align:center
as of late is called ZettaMovie.

00:02:45.081 --> 00:02:48.668 position:50% align:center
Once you sign up, you then
become a ZettaMovier.

00:02:48.752 --> 00:02:51.546 position:50% align:center
Which means each time
your video gets watched,

00:02:51.629 --> 00:02:53.590 position:50% align:center
you make a bit of cash.

00:02:53.673 --> 00:02:56.134 position:50% align:center
Okay, how much are
we talking per view?

00:02:56.217 --> 00:02:58.261 position:50% align:center
[ZERO-ONE]
Depends on your channel reps.

00:02:58.345 --> 00:03:00.722 position:50% align:center
The average rate has
gone down a little lately.

00:03:00.805 --> 00:03:03.808 position:50% align:center
But still, if a single view
gives you .1 yen,

00:03:03.892 --> 00:03:06.311 position:50% align:center
then a million means
a hundred thousand.

00:03:06.394 --> 00:03:09.898 position:50% align:center
So, why're you interested
in this suddenly, Makoto?

00:03:09.981 --> 00:03:12.984 position:50% align:center
Are you thinking about
promoting Kyouichi Ozaki?

00:03:13.068 --> 00:03:15.695 position:50% align:center
No. I have a
request from Takashi.

00:03:15.779 --> 00:03:17.072 position:50% align:center
It's G-Boys stuff.

00:03:17.155 --> 00:03:18.490 position:50% align:center
Turns out one of those
internet celebs

00:03:18.573 --> 00:03:20.492 position:50% align:center
is wanting to hire a bodyguard.

00:03:20.575 --> 00:03:23.578 position:50% align:center
I'm supposed to look into what
this guy is all about for him.

00:03:23.661 --> 00:03:24.829 position:50% align:center
That's interesting.

00:03:24.913 --> 00:03:26.664 position:50% align:center
I didn't know you guys
were watchdogs.

00:03:26.748 --> 00:03:29.668 position:50% align:center
Oh, and this joker
decided to tag along with me.

00:03:29.751 --> 00:03:31.127 position:50% align:center
I get to meet all kinds
of new people

00:03:31.211 --> 00:03:33.171 position:50% align:center
when I'm hanging with Makoto.

00:03:33.254 --> 00:03:34.964 position:50% align:center
And it's fun, so I've
been tailing the guy

00:03:35.048 --> 00:03:36.341 position:50% align:center
