a little brother, huh?

00:03:38.927 --> 00:03:40.470 position:50% align:center
Don't get any ideas.

00:03:40.553 --> 00:03:42.138 position:50% align:center
I figured it couldn't hurt
to keep the Red Angel's

00:03:42.222 --> 00:03:44.015 position:50% align:center
