00:05:10.977 --> 00:05:12.228 position:50% align:center
Oh?

00:05:12.312 --> 00:05:14.064 position:50% align:center
Check out the one I just made.

00:05:14.147 --> 00:05:16.441 position:50% align:center
I've already earned about
32 thousand yen.

00:05:18.401 --> 00:05:19.694 position:50% align:center
