00:06:07.701 --> 00:06:10.245 position:50% align:center
Why do you gorillas
keep negativin'.

00:06:10.328 --> 00:06:13.081 position:50% align:center
You think you're witty, but
your rhymes stay shitty!

00:06:13.164 --> 00:06:14.541 position:50% align:center
[MAKOTO]
Nice comeback.

00:06:14.624 --> 00:06:15.959 position:50% align:center
Well, they got angry.

00:06:16.042 --> 00:06:17.544 position:50% align:center
And that's not all.

00:06:17.627 --> 00:06:20.922 position:50% align:center
In four days, it's gonna be my
channel's five-year anniversary.

00:06:21.006 --> 00:06:22.841 position:50% align:center
So, they sent me this.

00:06:22.924 --> 00:06:25.969 position:50% align:center
[Z1] Here's an official present
from us to the onion whore.

00:06:26.052 --> 00:06:27.804 position:50% align:center
