to shoot it over here.

00:07:24.569 --> 00:07:26.821 position:50% align:center
[MAKOTO]
Wait, that's the Tokyo Met!

00:07:26.905 --> 00:07:29.282 position:50% align:center
[RYUUSEI] Everyone'll
talk about it for sure.

00:07:29.366 --> 00:07:32.827 position:50% align:center
