then it'll be totally cool.

00:07:32.911 --> 00:07:34.496 position:50% align:center
I can post rehab vids!

00:07:34.579 --> 00:07:35.789 position:50% align:center
[MAKOTO]
Sure...

00:07:35.872 --> 00:07:38.416 position:50% align:center
Look, pal, I'll be a
sitting duck for a while.

00:07:38.500 --> 00:07:40.919 position:50% align:center
