on your newest videos.

00:07:48.218 --> 00:07:49.302 position:50% align:center
[RYUUSEI]
You betcha.

00:07:49.386 --> 00:07:51.846 position:50% align:center
Even if they're
silly or pointless.

00:07:51.930 --> 00:07:54.057 position:50% align:center
There are thousands of
people out there who love

00:07:54.140 --> 00:07:55.892 position:50% align:center
everything that I'm doing.

00:07:55.975 --> 00:07:58.186 position:50% align:center
And I wouldn't give it up
for anything in the world!

00:07:58.269 --> 00:08:00.397 position:50% align:center
Books, magazines, TV.

00:08:00.480 --> 00:08:03.441 position:50% align:center
