contained universe.

00:08:03.525 --> 00:08:05.443 position:50% align:center
A perfectly cohesive story.

00:08:05.527 --> 00:08:07.612 position:50% align:center
One consistent
from start to finish.

00:08:07.696 --> 00:08:09.030 position:50% align:center
But on the internet,

00:08:09.114 --> 00:08:11.408 position:50% align:center
