everything making sense

00:08:11.491 --> 00:08:14.119 position:50% align:center
because it's just a
brief snapshot of life.

00:08:14.202 --> 00:08:16.287 position:50% align:center
Nope.
No scripts here, bro.

00:08:16.371 --> 00:08:19.082 position:50% align:center
It's about embracing the chaos
and rejecting the polished

00:08:19.165 --> 00:08:22.043 position:50% align:center
pretense of programming
for the real nitty-gritty!

00:08:22.127 --> 00:08:26.506 position:50% align:center
A fleeting, fragmentary,
livestream of love.

00:08:26.589 --> 00:08:30.176 position:50% align:center
The entire world is
going digital, baby!

00:08:30.260 --> 00:08:32.804 position:50% align:center
It's the dawn of a new age,
and it's unfolding

00:08:32.887 --> 00:08:34.889 position:50% align:center
before our very eyes.

00:08:34.973 --> 00:08:39.185 position:50% align:center
