as his guard detail.

00:09:17.474 --> 00:09:20.310 position:50% align:center
[MAKOTO] I'll stick close to
Ryuusei in the meantime.

00:09:20.393 --> 00:09:22.145 position:50% align:center
He and I are alike in many ways.

00:09:22.228 --> 00:09:24.230 position:50% align:center
